{"tid":1650651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再扭曲不分化不割蓆嘅意義","createTime":"2019-10-13T05:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T06:43:03.000Z","uid":4586,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4dafbea04a4816130e6a3ec240c50e1acb2fdcbf","tid":1650651,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆係講同路人，爭取目標時，對意見分歧同唔理想做法嘅態度，用互相包容去改進。將方向不斷反省同修改，以達到最大效益。<br />\n<br />\n並唔係指無條件接受認可己方人士行為！<br />\n<br />\n今次慶生同爭取民主係完全扯唔上關係，不分化不割蓆根本唔適用。<br />\n<br />\n係將來：<br />\n1. 如果行動方向偏差，例如破壞店鋪密度情況過火，應該保持理性，進行指點批判，但仍然抱持包容態度，共同進步。<br />\n<br />\n2. 行為與目標無關，如抗爭娛樂化、無意義違法行為及出於私利行為，必須即屌即割，以儆效尤。"},{"pid":"148d5a290bd836efbcb61e4a6f1b15e8695b8483","tid":1650651,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e185abebc90ba69d7ee95ad0b02b721c691aac0","tid":1650651,"uid":6594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"Sorry唔認同<br />\n我真係核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"cb4cbbfbe682a131bb8d89ee5df63d0d37376f4b","tid":1650651,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e185abebc90ba69d7ee95ad0b02b721c691aac0","tid":1650651,"uid":6594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"Sorry唔認同<br />\n我真係核爆都唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"無問題"},{"pid":"c8d3ae51e9801828e38f00096d1f5c315e15d13a","tid":1650651,"uid":197258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:44:45.000Z","msg":"冇人話認可<br />\n但唔需要不停狙擊"},{"pid":"9bb7c9534d931b2ed2010d32252d32530a692535","tid":1650651,"uid":271413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"帶返上正軌咪得，仲做既話就屌柒佢地"},{"pid":"fe1c7d4988b6d4cd83949989c2c7e7f751a65b64","tid":1650651,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8d3ae51e9801828e38f00096d1f5c315e15d13a","tid":1650651,"uid":197258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep